    <title>Syria contributor: Lorenzo Trombetta</title>
    <description>Lorenzo Trombetta is a Beirut-based journalist, Middle-Eastern senior correspondent for Italian News Agency Ansa. Specialized on contemporary Syria, he authored two monographies on this issue, focusing on the structure of the system of power in Baathist Syria. He regularly consults international organizations and national institutions on how to support civil society development in Syria.
</description>
